lead_paragraph: Hillary Rodham Clinton pointed to the 1990s as a time of broad-based prosperity under her husband, former President Bill Clinton, contrasting it Friday with policies under Republicans that she said promoted tax cuts for the wealthy and the emergence of "an entire shadow banking system."

headline.main: Hillary Clinton Recalls a Good Economy 1990s
headline.print_headline: Hillary Clinton Recalls a Good Economy 1990s
